org.hps.conditions.database

Class ConditionsSeriesConverter<ObjectType extends ConditionsObject,CollectionType extends ConditionsObjectCollection<ObjectType>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hps.conditions.database.ConditionsSeriesConverter<ObjectType,CollectionType>
  • Type Parameters:
    ObjectType - The type of the ConditionsObject.
    CollectionType - The type of the collection.

    final class ConditionsSeriesConverter<ObjectType extends ConditionsObject,CollectionType extends ConditionsObjectCollection<ObjectType>>
extends Object
    This converter creates a ConditionsSeries which is a list of ConditionsObjectCollection objects having the same type. This can be used to retrieve sets of conditions that may overlap in time validity. The user may then use whichever collections are of interest to them.
    See Also:
    ConditionsSeries, ConditionsObjectCollection, ConditionsObject, DatabaseConditionsManager
